snippet.title: Top Spin 4 - Legends Trailer
snippet.description:
Top Spin 4 has an extensive list of legends from yesteryear including Pete Sampras, Boris Becker, Bjorn Bork, Ivan Lendl, Michael Chang, Jim Courier, Patrick Rafter and, of course, Andre Agassi. Relive the greatest match-ups or make some of your own. Get Vintage Agassi only when you pre-order at Gamestop. Buy it now - http://www.2ksports.com/preorder/topspin4.

Top Spin 4 is available in stores 3/15/2011, 3/18/2011 internationally. ESRB Rating: Everyone
